{"content": "I need to multiply 860 \u00d7 846 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 860\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 6\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 6\u00d79 + 0 = 648 + 54 + 0 = 702\u2081\u2080\n- 846\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 6 = 648 + 36 + 6 = 690\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 702 \u00d7 690 = 484,380\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 484380 \u00f7 9 = 53820 r 0\n- 53820 \u00f7 9 = 5980 r 0\n- 5980 \u00f7 9 = 664 r 4\n- 664 \u00f7 9 = 73 r 7\n- 73 \u00f7 9 = 8 r 1\n- 8 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 8\n\nReading from bottom to top: **817400\u2089**\n\n817400", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 340}